tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE survey_feedback (
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    rating INT
)

CREATE TABLE SurveyResults (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    response_id INT,
    result_value DECIMAL,
    FOREIGN KEY (survey_id) REFERENCES SurveyResponses(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (response_id) REFERENCES SurveyResponses(id)
);

CREATE TABLE responses (
    response_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT REFERENCES surveys (survey_id),
    respondent_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    response_text TEXT,
    response_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE analysis (
    analysis_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT REFERENCES surveys (survey_id),
    analyst_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    analysis_text TEXT,
    analysis_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE survey_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_id INT,
  question_id INT,
  participant_id INT,
  response_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    respondent_name VARCHAR(50),
    response_text TEXT,
    response_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE responses_ratings (
    response_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    rating INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (response_id) REFERENCES survey_responses(response_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (question_id) REFERENCES questions(question_id)
);

CREATE TABLE survey_participants (
    survey_id INT,
    participant_id INT,
    participant_name VARCHAR(50),
    registration_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (survey_id) REFERENCES surveys(survey_id)
);
